                <head>289. Minutes of a National Security Council Review Group Meeting<note n="1"
                        type="source" xml:id="d289fn1">Source: National Archives, Nixon Presidential
                        Materials, <gloss target="#t_NSC_1">NSC</gloss> Files, <gloss
                            target="#t_NSC_1">NSC</gloss> Institutional Files (H-Files), Box H–111,
                        Senior Review Group, <gloss target="#t_SRG_1">SRG</gloss> Minutes Originals
                        1970. Secret. The meeting was held in the White House Situation Room.</note>
                </head>
                <opener>
                    <dateline rendition="#right">
                        <placeName>Washington</placeName>, <date calendar="gregorian"
                            from="1970-01-16T14:50:00-05:00" to="1970-01-16T17:55:00-05:00">January
                            16, 1970, 2:50–3:55 p.m.</date>
                    </dateline>
                </opener>
                <list type="subject">
                    <head>SUBJECT</head>
                    <item>U.S. Policy Toward Spain (<gloss target="#t_NSSM_1">NSSM</gloss> 46)<note
                            n="2" xml:id="d289fn2">
                            <ref target="#d279">Document 279</ref>.</note>
                    </item>
                </list>
                <list type="participants">
                    <head>PARTICIPATION</head>
